snippet.title: Codemasters Collection 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured directly from the OG Evercade handheld. This cart contains 17 games.

Games on the cart:
00:00:09 - Bee 52 (NES)
00:05:50 - Big Nose Freaks Out (NES)
00:11:38 - Big Nose the Caveman (NES)
00:15:57 - Boomerang Kid (NES)
00:19:13 - CJ's Elephant Antics (NES)
00:23:08 - Cannon Fodder (MegaDrive / Genesis)
00:34:26 - Cosmic Spacehead (MegaDrive / Genesis)
00:43:33 - F-16 Renegade (NES)
00:45:48 - Linus Spacehead (NES)
00:50:41 - Mega-Lo-Mania (MegaDrive / Genesis)
01:01:49 - MiG 29: Soviet Fighter (NES)
01:05:24 - Psycho Pinball (MegaDrive / Genesis)
01:09:19 - Sensible Soccer (MegaDrive / Genesis)
01:15:59 - Stunt Buggies (NES)
01:18:42 - Super Skidmarks (MegaDrive / Genesis)
01:22:17 - Tennis All Stars (MegaDrive / Genesis)*
01:27:06 - The Ultimate Stuntman (NES)

*Previously unreleased game (It was repurposed into an officially licensed Pete Sampras Tennis game, but this version has plenty of differences)
